query: synchromouse a game of improvised joint action
sql:

    p.paper_id,
    p.title,
    p.abstract,
    p.venue,
    p.year,
    p.citation_count
FROM Papers p

    to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '') || ' ' || coalesce(p.abstract, ''))

query: efficient sampling of dependency structure
sql:
SELECT
  p.paper_id,
  p.title,
  p.abstract,
  p.venue,
  p.year,
  p.citation_count
FROM Papers p
WHERE
  (p.title ILIKE '%efficient%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%efficient%')
  AND (p.title ILIKE '%sampling%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%sampling%')
  AND (
    p.title ILIKE '%dependency structure%'
    OR p.abstract ILIKE '%dependency structure%'
    OR (
      (p.title ILIKE '%dependency%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%dependency%')
      AND (p.title ILIKE '%structure%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%structure%')
    )
  )
ORDER BY
  ((CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%efficient%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%efficient%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%sampling%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%sampling%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%dependency structure%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%dependency structure%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%dependency%' THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%dependency%' THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%structure%' THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%structure%' THEN 0.5 ELSE 0 END)
  ) DESC,
  p.citation_count DESC NULLS LAST,
  p.year DESC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 100

      OR ((p.title ILIKE '%neural%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%neural%')
          AND (p.title ILIKE '%machine%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%machine%')
          AND (p.title ILIKE '%translation%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%translation%'))
    )
  )
ORDER BY
  CASE
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%convolutional encoder%' AND p.title ILIKE '%neural machine translation%' THEN 1
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%convolutional encoder%' AND (p.title ILIKE '%translation%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%translation%') THEN 2
    WHEN (p.title ILIKE '%convolutional%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%convolutional%')
         AND (p.title ILIKE '%encoder%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%encoder%')
         AND (p.title ILIKE '%neural machine translation%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%neural machine translation%') THEN 3
    WHEN (p.title ILIKE '%convolutional%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%convolutional%')
         AND (p.title ILIKE '%encoder%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%encoder%') THEN 4
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%neural machine translation%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%neural machine translation%' THEN 5
    ELSE 6
  END,
  p.citation_count DESC NULLS LAST,
  p.year DESC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 100

query: infonice easy creation of information graphics
sql:
SELECT
  p.paper_id,
  p.title,
  p.abstract,
  p.venue,
  p.year,
  p.citation_count
FROM Papers p
WHERE
  (p.title ILIKE '%infonice%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%infonice%')
  OR (p.title ILIKE '%information graphic%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%information graphic%')
  OR (p.title ILIKE '%information graphics%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%information graphics%')
  OR (p.title ILIKE '%infographic%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%infographic%')
  OR (p.title ILIKE '%infographics%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%infographics%')
  OR (
    (p.title ILIKE '%information%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%information%')
    AND (p.title ILIKE '%graphic%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%graphic%')
  )
  OR (
    (p.title ILIKE '%easy%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%easy%')
    AND (p.title ILIKE '%creation%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%creation%')
  )
ORDER BY
  ((CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%infonice%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%infonice%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%information graphic%' OR p.title ILIKE '%information graphics%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%information graphic%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%information graphics%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.title ILIKE '%infographic%' OR p.title ILIKE '%infographics%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%infographic%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%infographics%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN (p.title ILIKE '%easy%' AND p.title ILIKE '%creation%') THEN 2 ELSE 0 END) +
   (CASE WHEN (p.abstract ILIKE '%easy%' AND p.abstract ILIKE '%creation%') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
  ) DESC,
  p.citation_count DESC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 100

query: karamad a voicebased crowdsourcing platform for underserved populations
sql:
SELECT
  p.paper_id,
  p.title,
  p.abstract,
  p.venue,
  p.year,
  p.citation_count
FROM Papers p
LEFT JOIN PaperAuthors pa ON p.paper_id = pa.paper_id
LEFT JOIN Authors a ON pa.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE
  to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '') || ' ' || coalesce(p.abstract, '')) @@ plainto_tsquery('english', 'karamad voicebased crowdsourcing platform underserved populations')
  OR a.name ILIKE '%karamad%'
ORDER BY
  ts_rank_cd(
    to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '') || ' ' || coalesce(p.abstract, '')),
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'karamad voicebased crowdsourcing platform underserved populations')
  ) DESC,
  p.citation_count DESC
LIMIT 100
